│ allowing normal min/max folding for regular icmp instructions. The edit should be inserted at line 5618, right   │
│ after the existing signedness checks.\n\n5. Conclusion: By adding this guard, we prevent incorrect               │
│ transformations of `samesign` icmp instructions while preserving all existing functionality for regular          │
│ comparisons. This is a conservative but safe fix that addresses the root cause without affecting other           │
│ optimizations."})                                                                                                │
